(Project Atlas: Technical Overview) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Project Atlas is an internal data-platform initiative kicked off in) Tj T*
(March 2026. The platform unifies telemetry from three subsystems:) Tj T*
(ingestion, storage, and query routing. It targets sub-second p99) Tj T*
(latency for analytical queries on datasets up to 10 TB.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The lead architect is Priya Raman. Engineering is split across two) Tj T*
(pods: Pod Echo handles ingestion and Pod Foxtrot handles query.) Tj T*
ET
