(Architecture and Storage) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Atlas uses a columnar storage layer based on Apache Parquet, with) Tj T*
(a metadata service backed by FoundationDB. Compaction runs every) Tj T*
(six hours and emits Prometheus metrics on the namespace) Tj T*
(atlas.compaction.*.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Hot data lives in NVMe-backed nodes; cold data tiers to S3 after) Tj T*
(30 days. Replication factor is 3 in the hot tier.) Tj T*
ET
endstream
>>
