(Operational Notes) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(On-call rotation is weekly. The runbook lives at docs/atlas/runbook.md.) Tj T*
(Page severity is set by the SEV field in PagerDuty: SEV1 pages the) Tj T*
(primary oncall and the architect; SEV3 only emails the team list.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Known issue: query routing occasionally misroutes when a tenant has) Tj T*
(more than 2,000 partitions. Workaround is documented in JIRA-4421.) Tj T*
